      "content": "people \"find meaning\" when they still have a foundation to stand on. i don't. it's like... i'm standing in a crater. the person who could actually do things, who had a brain worth listening to, died when that theory collapsed. what's the point in just \"being a human\" when that human is an empty shell?",
